  m_text: "This page will show the avatar customizer, allowing you to change five
    attributes, i.e., skin tone, age, weight, gender, and height. \n \nYou can choose
    the attribute you want to change by clicking the up and down arrow. \n\nBefore
    you can continue, you need to change every attribute by providing input pressing
    the right arrow key or indicate that you don't want to change the attribute.   
    \n\nPlease note that no customization choices you make affect gameplay. "
